Class Move

  • java.lang.Object
    • testModel.Move

  • public class Move
extends java.lang.Object
    Type: Move
    Package:testModel
    This class tries to encapsulate the essence of a move for the noughts and crosses game. It has a X-coordinate a Y-coordinate and a player token. These are set on creation of a move object. This class provides getter methods for the X-coordinate, Y-coordinate and player token.
    Author:
    {}rpheus
